Package pegasus.tuple

Interface IntTuple

All Superinterfaces:
BaseTuple<Integer>, IndexedIntIterable, Iterable<Integer>, Serializable
All Known Implementing Classes:
IntArrayTuple, IntPair, IntTriple
public interface IntTuple extends BaseTuple<Integer>, IndexedIntIterable
A value-based primitive tuple of int values.
